---
const posts = [
  {
    title: "Blog in arrivo 01",
    category: "Strategia",
    excerpt:
      "Qui comparirà un articolo dedicato a idee, crescita, progetti e visione del blog.",
  },
  {
    title: "Blog in arrivo 02",
    category: "Business",
    excerpt:
      "Uno spazio pensato per contenuti più professionali, chiari e ordinati da leggere.",
  },
  {
    title: "Blog in arrivo 03",
    category: "Tecnologia",
    excerpt:
      "Articoli su siti web, strumenti digitali, sviluppo e costruzione di progetti online.",
  },
  {
    title: "Blog in arrivo 04",
    category: "Lifestyle",
    excerpt:
      "Una sezione dove potrai pubblicare riflessioni, racconti e contenuti più personali.",
  },
  {
    title: "Blog in arrivo 05",
    category: "Marketing",
    excerpt:
      "Spazio per idee su comunicazione, branding, contenuti e presenza online.",
  },
  {
    title: "Blog in arrivo 06",
    category: "Crescita",
    excerpt:
      "Un blocco dedicato a pensieri, lezioni e articoli che vorrai aggiungere col tempo.",
  },
];
---

<html lang="it">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Blog Manuel</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Blog professionale scuro con home moderna e sezioni articoli."
    />

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #050505;
        --panel: #0c0c0f;
        --panel-2: #111116;
        --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        --text: #f5f5f5;
        --muted: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
        --soft: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        --accent: #ffffff;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent 30%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #050505 0%, #09090b 100%);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Display", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .container {
        width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .nav {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 50;
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        background: rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.7);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .nav-inner {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 18px 0;
      }

      .brand-top {
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: 0.3em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .brand-name {
        margin-top: 4px;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 22px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover {
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 84px 0 48px;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
        gap: 32px;
        align-items: end;
      }

      .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: 0.22em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 18px 0 0;
        font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 78px);
        line-height: 0.96;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      }

      .hero p {
        max-width: 720px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 14px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-top: 28px;
      }

      .btn-primary,
      .btn-secondary {
        padding: 14px 20px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        transition: 0.25s ease;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        background: white;
        color: black;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .btn-secondary {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
        color: white;
      }

      .btn-secondary:hover {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      }

      .hero-panel {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 28px;
        padding: 22px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      }

      .hero-panel-top {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      .mini-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .mini-card span {
        font-size: 11px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .mini-card h3 {
        margin: 10px 0 8px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .mini-card p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .section {
        padding: 56px 0 90px;
      }

      .section-head {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 24px;
        align-items: end;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: 0.28em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h2 {
        margin: 10px 0 0;
        font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      }

      .section-copy {
        color: var(--muted);
        max-width: 560px;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .card {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 28px;
        padding: 24px;
        background:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
        transition: transform 0.35s ease, border-color 0.35s ease, background 0.35s ease;
      }

      .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-6px);
        border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
        background:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.07), rgba(255,255,255,0.03));
      }

      .card::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: auto -40px -40px auto;
        width: 120px;
        height: 120px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
        filter: blur(8px);
      }

      .card-top {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 12px;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .card-category {
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .card h3 {
        margin: 18px 0 12px;
        font-size: 24px;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      .card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.8;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .card-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-top: 22px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: white;
      }

      .about-box {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
        padding: 70px 0 90px;
      }

      .about-inner {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 28px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      .about-inner p {
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.9;
        margin: 0;
      }

      footer {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
        color: var(--muted);
        padding: 26px 0 40px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .reveal {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(34px);
        transition:
          opacity 0.8s ease,
          transform 0.8s ease;
        will-change: transform, opacity;
      }

      .reveal.show {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }

      @media (max-width: 960px) {
        .hero-grid,
        .about-inner,
        .grid,
        .section-head {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .section-head {
          display: grid;
        }

        .nav-links {
          display: none;
        }

        .hero {
          padding-top: 54px;
        }

        .grid {
          gap: 16px;
        }

        .card h3 {
          font-size: 22px;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .container {
          width: min(100% - 20px, 1120px);
        }

        h1 {
          line-height: 1;
        }

        .hero p {
          font-size: 16px;
        }

        .hero-panel,
        .card {
          border-radius: 22px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="nav">
      <div class="container nav-inner">
        <div>
          <div class="brand-top">Blog</div>
          <div class="brand-name">Blog Manuel</div>
        </div>

        <nav class="nav-links">
          <a href="#home">Home</a>
          <a href="#blogs">Blogs</a>
          <a href="#about">About</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero container" id="home">
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="reveal">
            <div class="badge">Sito blog professionale</div>
            <h1>Un blog nero, elegante e moderno costruito per crescere.</h1>
            <p>
              Questa home è pensata per mostrare i tuoi contenuti in blocchi puliti,
              con uno stile premium e animazioni morbide quando scorri la pagina.
            </p>

            <div class="hero-actions">
              <a href="#blogs" class="btn-primary">Scopri i blog</a>
              <a href="#about" class="btn-secondary">Scopri il progetto</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-panel reveal">
            <div class="hero-panel-top">
              <span>In evidenza</span>
              <span>Home iniziale</span>
            </div>

            <div class="mini-card">
              <span>Design</span>
              <h3>Stile scuro professionale</h3>
              <p>Impatto visivo forte, leggibilità alta e struttura moderna.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mini-card">
              <span>Animazione</span>
              <h3>Comparsa lenta allo scroll</h3>
              <p>Le sezioni entrano in pagina in modo fluido e pulito.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mini-card">
              <span>Base pronta</span>
              <h3>Blog a blocchi</h3>
              <p>Ogni card potrà poi collegarsi a un vero articolo scritto da te.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section container" id="blogs">
        <div class="section-head reveal">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Ultimi blog</div>
            <h2>I contenuti che pubblicherai qui</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="section-copy">
            Una griglia elegante in cui ogni blocco rappresenta un articolo del tuo blog.
            Per ora sono segnaposto, poi li sostituiremo con i tuoi veri post.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
          {posts.map((post) => (
            <article class="card reveal">
              <div class="card-top">
                <span class="card-category">{post.category}</span>
                <span>In arrivo</span>
              </div>

              <h3>{post.title}</h3>
              <p>{post.excerpt}</p>

              <div class="card-link">
                <span>Aprirà qui</span>
                <span>→</span>
              </div>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-box" id="about">
        <div class="container about-inner">
          <div class="reveal">
            <div class="eyebrow">About</div>
            <h2>Una base premium per il tuo progetto.</h2>
          </div>

          <p class="reveal">
            Questa è una prima home professionale: nera, pulita, con movimento allo scroll
            e blocchi pensati per ospitare i tuoi futuri articoli. Nel prossimo passaggio
            possiamo aggiungere pagine singole, immagini copertina, footer vero, SEO e
            collegamento automatico ai post reali.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div class="container">© 2026 Blog Manuel. Tutti i diritti riservati.</div>
    </footer>

    <script>
      const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
        (entries) => {
          entries.forEach((entry) => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
              entry.target.classList.add("show");
            }
          });
        },
        {
          threshold: 0.14,
        }
      );

      document.querySelectorAll(".reveal").forEach((el) => {
        observer.observe(el);
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>